    leaflet
Description: Fits Bayesian spatio-temporal models and makes predictions on stream networks using the approach by Santos-Fernandez, Edgar, et al. (2022)."Bayesian spatio-temporal models for stream networks" and Santos-Fernandez, Edgar, et al. (2023). "SSNbayes: An R Package for Bayesian Spatio-Temporal Modelling on Stream Networks". In these models, spatial dependence is captured using stream distance and flow connectivity, while temporal autocorrelation is modelled using vector autoregression methods. 
